{"tid":1628032,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【抗暴之戰】太子站「五七拜祭」：義士終於意識自己己死亡","createTime":"2019-10-05T21:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T11:23:37.000Z","uid":226548,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3f3dfb177485ff956c788a406219c75c2528e3f5","tid":1628032,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T21:09:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191005/large/1570271793_b54c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191005%2Flarge%2F1570271793_b54c.jpg&h=19e8dd9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網絡一直流傳8.31太子站有市民被打死，但港鐵拒絕公開閉路電視，一批市民於8月31日的35日後，今日聚集於旺角警署外摺疊大量金銀衣紙，準備太陽下山後，稱為死者進行五七拜祭。根據習俗，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人死去第三十五日即是五七，死者會意識自己終於死亡。</strong></span>有市民認為港鐵一直拒絕公開CCTV，確信831有打死人，即使他日港鐵終願公開，能否交代當日真相亦令人質疑。"},{"pid":"1a3598181600b70eee93a5d5e060966fbd227629","tid":1628032,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T21:09:40.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191005/60121620\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191005%2F60121620&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfEA%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=ca2d0150\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191005%2F60121620&h=32426db8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191005/60121620</a>"},{"pid":"387ff7fed768093be394ebbb200395fb448f29ec","tid":1628032,"uid":181697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T21:50:26.000Z","msg":"沈重既消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手足安心上路喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁被自殺既呢..？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor